---
import SocialMediaBtns from "../buttons/SocialMediaBtns.astro";
---

<section id="contact" class="section-shell py-20">
  <div class="glass-panel subtle-border relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl px-6 py-10 sm:px-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400/12 via-transparent to-amber-400/12"></div>
    <div class="relative grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_.9fr] lg:items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-teal-400">Contacto</p>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Listo para convertir ideas en productos</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
          Cu√©ntame sobre tu proyecto, una mejora pendiente o un proceso que quieras automatizar.
          Coordino reuniones breves para definir el alcance y proponer un roadmap claro.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:trabajoluisaraya@gmail.com">
            Escribir un correo
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 12l-4-4-4 4m8 0l-4 4-4-4" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            class="btn-ghost"
            href="https://wa.me/56974022976?text=Hola%20Luis,%20vi%20tu%20portafolio%20y%20quiero%20conversar."
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Abrir WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-color)] bg-white/5 p-5">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-0.5 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_0_6px_rgba(74,222,128,0.18)]"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Correo</p>
            <a class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]" href="mailto:trabajoluisaraya@gmail.com">
              trabajoluisaraya@gmail.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-0.5 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-sky-400 shadow-[0_0_0_6px_rgba(56,189,248,0.18)]"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--text-secondary)]">WhatsApp</p>
            <a
              class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]"
              href="https://wa.me/56974022976?text=Hola%20Luis,%20vi%20tu%20portafolio%20y%20quiero%20conversar."
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              +56 9 7402 2976
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--text-secondary)]">O en redes</span>
          <SocialMediaBtns />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
